{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"--cur is useful for testing different AI tools without affecting default settings.\nOverrides --cfg for the current session only.\nExample: `x agent --cur set zero_harness=codex` then `x agent request \"test\"` — uses codex without changing defaults\n"
,
"cn"
:
"--cur 适合临时测试不同 AI 工具，不影响默认配置。\n仅覆盖当前会话的 --cfg 配置。\n示例: `x agent --cur set zero_harness=codex` 然后 `x agent request \"test\"` —— 临时用 codex，不改动默认设置\n"
}
]
,
"set"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"设置临时配置值"
,
"en"
:
"Set temporary configuration values"
}
,
"zero_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"临时默认 AI 工具"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary default AI tool"
}
}
,
"one_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"临时备选 AI 工具"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary alternative AI tool"
}
}
,
"#n"
:
{
