}
}
}
]
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cur set zero_harness=kimi-cli"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 临时切换到 kimi-cli（仅当前终端）"
,
"en"
:
